window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With <i>The Clearing</i>, Southeastern Booksellers Award winner Tim Gautreaux delivers a brutal novel of love, family, and redemption. </p> <p>Randolph Aldridge travels to a snake-infested Cypress mill in Louisiana to find his brother Byron, a troubled veteran of World War I. Once there, Randolph finds that By is a shell of his former self—and that the murderous cartel controlling the mill’s casino won’t give them any peace.</p>"; 
